Here is a look at key events in the student

May 13 _ About 2,000 students begin a hunger strike in Tiananmen Square.
May 14 _ Thousands flock to the square to back the students.
May 15 _ The government deadline for students to leave the square passes.
May 16 _ Hundreds of thousands occupy the square.
May 17 _ Zhao pleas for students to leave.
Li also visits the students briefly.
The students later decide to end the hunger strike.
May 27 _ Beijing student leaders propose students end their occupation of Tiananmen Square.
Non-Beijing students resist and the sit-in continues.
